Mass. Gen. Laws Ann. ch. 185C, \u00a7 16.raw_text: Mass. Gen. Laws Ann. ch. 185C, § 16 and ch. 218, § 19.
Mass. Gen. Laws Ann. ch. 185C, \u00a7 16.proposition: Jurisdiction is proper in this Court pursuant to Mass. Gen. Laws Ann. ch. 185C, § 16 and ch. 218, § 19.

Mass. Gen. Laws Ann. ch. 186, \u00a7 14..proposition: Defendant's failure to promptly address the electrical issues in the affected bedroom constitutes a breach of the implied covenant of quiet enjoyment, a violation of Mass. Gen. Laws Ann. ch. 186, § 14.
